---
const navigation = [
  { name: '홈', href: '/' },
  { name: '연락처', href: '/contact' },
];
---

<footer class="bg-dark-gray border-t border-secondary/20 py-16 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-[100rem] mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {/* Company Info */}
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">대한카고크레인</h3>
        <p class="font-paragraph text-secondary-foreground mb-4">
          믿을 수 있는 중량물 운송 및 장비 연계 서비스
        </p>
        <p class="font-paragraph text-secondary-foreground text-sm">
          안전하고 신속한 운송 솔루션으로<br />
          고객의 성공적인 프로젝트를 지원합니다.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Quick Links */}
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold mb-4">빠른 링크</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          {navigation.map((item) => (
            <li>
              <a
                href={item.href}
                class="font-paragraph text-secondary-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors"
              >
                {item.name}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      {/* Contact Info */}
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold mb-4">연락처</h4>
        <div class="space-y-2 font-paragraph text-secondary-foreground">
          <p>
            <span class="text-foreground">전화:</span>{' '}
            <a href="tel:010-2332-4822" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">
              010-2332-4822
            </a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="text-foreground">이메일:</span>{' '}
            <a href="mailto:kkh2772@naver.com" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">
              kkh2772@naver.com
            </a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="text-foreground">주소:</span><br />
            대구광역시 동구 신암남로 145(신암동)
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="text-foreground">사업자번호:</span>{' '}
            141-22-02126
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="text-foreground">대표자:</span>{' '}
            곽미경
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-secondary/20 mt-12 pt-8 text-center">
      <p class="font-paragraph text-secondary-foreground text-sm">
        © 2024 대한카고크레인. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
